    marketValue: "60 gp",
    components: ["1x Pouch of Dust (Celestial)"],
    stats: "This dwarven smithing hammer has runes running from end to end. When beaten against an anvil, the runes around the hammer glow a bright red and emanate heat, allowing a blacksmith to use the hammer to mold weapons and armor using only the hammer and anvil.\nTop to Bottom: Redsmith Crucible Set,\nRedsmith Hammer, Rejuvenating Draft",
    tags: ["Griffon's Saddlebag"]
