    attunement: "Yes",
    baseDC: 0,
    baseTime: 0,
    requiredCheck: "Spellcasting Ability (Medicine)",
    marketValue: "30 gp",
    components: ["1x Eye (Humanoid)"],
    stats: "This silver coin is embossed with the trickster dragon Duvra on one side (heads), and a sailing ship on the other (tails). Whenever you or another creature you can see flips this coin, you can control whether it lands heads, tails, or on its side.\nLeft to Right: Silver Eagle Studded Cuirass, Shimmering Spectacles,\nShifter's Shine, Silver Corn of Duvra",
