    stats: "A carved walking stick with a handle wrapped in worn leather, this magic staff gives you better endurance. While you use this staff as a walking stick while traveling on foot, you have advantage on the first save you make to endure a forced march.\nTop to Bottom: Stalwart Staff,\nStalagmite Geode, Status Signets",
