    marketValue: "30 gp",
    components: ["1x Phial of Blood (Giant)"],
    stats: "These silver rings often come in pairs and indicate the well-being of its wearer. If you and another friendly creature you can see are wearing these rings within 100 feet of each other, you are magically aware of the other creature’s current number of hit points and condition.",
