    stats: "This elegant, dark dagger is never bloodstained and effortlessly pierces flesh. You gain a +1 bonus to attack and damage rolls made with this magic weapon.\nWhen this dagger is used by an evil-aligned creature, any creature hit by it doesn’t bleed from the attack or the wound it leaves behind for 10 minutes.\nLeft to right: Bloodthirster Scimitar, Bloodshard Trident, Bloodthirsty Bistoury",
    tags: ["Griffon's Saddlebag"]
