    metatag: "Badger",
    stats: "This weighty blade carries with it the strength of the mighty badger. You gain a +1 bonus to attack and damage rolls made with this magic weapon. The sword has 3 charges and regains all expended charges daily at dawn. When you hit a Large or smaller creature with this weapon, you can expend 1 charge from it to push that creature 5 feet away from you.",
