    stats: "When you drink this potion, you regain 1d3 + 1 (uncommon), 1d4 + 3 (rare), 1d6 + 4 (very rare), or all (legendary) spent Hit Dice. When you drink the legendary variant of a rejuvenating draft, your age is reduced by 1d4 years (to a minimum of 1 year old).",
    tags: ["Griffon's Saddlebag"]
